        "content": "<p>I used <code>is_scalar_tower</code> instead of <code>module.comp_hom</code>, this works better with the case that <code>R = ‚Ñ§</code> since you don't need to show that the module structure from <code>comp_hom</code> matches with the natural <code>‚Ñ§</code>-module structure on any ring.</p>",
